com.microsoft.bingads.v13.bulk.entities

Class BulkFeedItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.internal.bulk.BulkObject
      • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.bulk.entities.BulkEntity
        • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.internal.bulk.entities.SingleRecordBulkEntity
          • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.bulk.entities.BulkFeedItem

  • public class BulkFeedItem
extends SingleRecordBulkEntity
    Represents a Feed Item that can be read or written in a bulk file.

    Properties of this class and of classes that it is derived from, correspond to fields of the Feed Item record in a bulk file. For more information, see Feed Item at https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=846127.

    See Also:
    BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter
